# SVGAttribute
2D graphics primitives are rendered using SVG elements. To apply raw SVG attributes to a primitive use `SVGAttribute`:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
# SVGAttribute
2D graphics primitives are rendered using SVG elements. To apply raw SVG attributes to a primitive use `SVGAttribute`:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Graphics[{
  Red, Disk[{-0.2,-0.2},0.4], 
  SVGAttribute[
    Disk[{0,0},0.3], 
    "style"->"filter: drop-shadow(-3px 10px 4px #4444dd); fill:blue;"
  ]
}]

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
(*VB[*)(Graphics[{RGBColor[1, 0, 0], Disk[{-0.2, -0.2}, 0.4], SVGAttribute[Disk[{0, 0}, 0.3], "style" -> "filter: drop-shadow(-3px 10px 4px #4444dd); fill:blue;"]}])(*,*)(*"1:eJxTTMoPSmNkYGAoZgESHvk5KRAeB5BwL0osyMhMLk5jhsn7ZBaXQHgg+SB3J+f8nPyiTJCOTAYYkcYEU+6SWZyN4IE0F82aCQIn96MzbtpDFPIAieAwd8eSkqLMpNKSVHyGIawsMgaDy/YIBUGlOanBrCBeSSWQZQZyWGZOSWqRlUJKUX6BbnFGYkp+uYaucUGFgqEBkDABYmUTIEhJ0bRWAKrNsUrKKU21BgABNUlc"*)(*]VB*)

