.md
Use can group multiple elements into a low-level SVG group and apply a CSS filter:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Use can group multiple elements into a low-level SVG group and apply a CSS filter:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Graphics[
	SVGAttribute[
		SVGGroup[{
			Red, Disk[{0,0}, 0.5],
			Blue, Line[{{-1,-1}, {1,1}}]
		}]
	, "style"->"filter: blur(10px)"]
]

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
(*VB[*)(Graphics[SVGAttribute[SVGGroup[{RGBColor[1, 0, 0], Disk[{0, 0}, 0.5], RGBColor[0, 0, 1], Line[{{-1, -1}, {1, 1}}]}], "style" -> "filter: blur(10px)"]])(*,*)(*"1:eJxTTMoPSmNkYGAoZgESHvk5KRAeB5BwL0osyMhMLk5jAonwAIngMHfHkpKizKTSklSEOqCoe1F+aUEaC8wcn8zikjRmmHyQu5Nzfk5+USZIRyYDjIAYC1LuklmcjeCBNCNUFTGAwQN7LObBFYFNRnjDJzMvFdU8NNP/AwGYQBNnhJsFFw8qzUkNZgXxSiqBLCGQZGZOSWqRlUJSTmmRhqFBQYUmAN6nQ+k="*)(*]VB*)

